A very good recipe. Only my Italian father makes better meatballs. As always, the meatballs were better the next day after spending a night in the sauce. But I had a bit of a problem w/ the bread crumbs... there turned out to be a few bread chunks in the meatballs. Next time I would chop up the bread a bit before adding the milk and would spend more time mushing it up before combining it w/ the meat (esp. the crust). I made the sauce w/o the sausage and it was still great. Definitely a keeper (at least until I get my dad's recipe!) :-)

