To the cook from San Fran--I bake meatball for appetizers by taking white bread, placing it on a cookie sheet. I maked depressions in it with my fingers and place a meatball in the depression. Then bake at 350 until cooked. This way the grease goes into the bread. Don't see why this technique wouldn't work here.

